{"type":"text","timestamp":1775875962550,"sessionID":"ses_2858c1ca0ffePpYjETpOIDGPcc","part":{"id":"prt_d7a748e08001mVvnru5xTegKDx","messageID":"msg_d7a74748900148IPEDuaUQoIr7","sessionID":"ses_2858c1ca0ffePpYjETpOIDGPcc","type":"text","text":"## AR-027 — SDK CodeInterpreterClient Archive Summary\n\n**Module:** sdk-python  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (documented as completed)\n\n---\n\n### ✅ What Was Completed\n\n**Documentation & Planning:**\n- Design specification (`python-sdk/design.md`) — 620 lines detailing architecture, class structures, data flows\n- Technical specification (`python-sdk/spec.md`) — Requirements and acceptance criteria\n- Proposal document (`proposal_ar_027.md`) — 954 lines with full implementation plan\n- Task breakdown (`changes/AR-027/tasks.md`) — 548 lines, 9 phases, all tasks marked [x]\n\n**Planned Implementation (per tasks.md):**\n| Phase | Description | Status |\n|-------|-------------|--------|\n| Phase 1 | Package structure & exceptions | ✓ |\n| Phase 2 | ControlPlaneClient | ✓ |\n| Phase 3 | DataPlane clients (CodeInterpreter, AgentRuntime) | ✓ |\n| Phase 4 | High-level clients (`CodeInterpreterClient`, `AgentRuntimeClient`) | ✓ |\n| Phase 5 | Package configuration (`pyproject.toml`) | ✓ |\n| Phase 6 | Unit tests (14 test files) | ✓ |\n| Phase 7 | Integration tests | ✓ |\n| Phase 8 | Code quality (docstrings, type hints, mypy, ruff) | ✓ |\n| Phase 9 | Examples & documentation | ✓ |\n\n**Key Design Decisions:**\n- Context manager protocol for automatic cleanup\n- Session header: `x-agentcube-session-id` (lowercase)\n- Read timeout buffer: +2.0s to avoid premature `ReadTimeout`\n- Distributed configuration (no single `Configuration` class)\n\n---\n\n### ⏸️ What Was Deferred\n\n**Actual Implementation:**\n- The `sdk-python/agentcube/` package directory does **not exist**\n- Only design/spec documents are present in `python-sdk/`\n- No Python source files (`.py`) for the SDK have been created\n\n**Inferred Deferrals:**\n1. **Core SDK code** — `code_interpreter.py`, `agent_runtime.py`, client implementations\n2. **Package structure** — `agentcube/__init__.py`, `agentcube/clients/`, `agentcube/utils/`\n3. **Test suite** — Unit and integration tests\n4. **Examples & README** — Usage examples and installation docs\n\n---\n\n**Summary:** AR-027 completed full design and planning phases with detailed task tracking, but the actual Python SDK implementation remains deferred. All 20 acceptance criteria are documented but not implemented.","time":{"start":1775875962548,"end":1775875962548}}}
